parameters:
Wait, don't talk to me...! I'm almost done making the
strongest snowman...!!
\SE[0]First, we need to accomplish our objective...

Hey girls, you look cold! We're used to it, so it's no big
deal for us!! ...Just kidding! We get scared of the cold
wave every year!!

Yay! It's snow! Snowball fight! Snow hut! Sledding! Huge
icicle! Snowman! Snow-viewing daifuku!!

...I'm bored. I want to indulge in adult and dirty
activities in the city, like in Yuriseen or Codain!

There's a magician living beyond this cave. They're a very
kind and beautiful person, strong too... I hope one day I
can become an adult like them...

Welcome to Yukiifuru! Traveler-san! Oh, don't worry, this
girl won't bite! She's my 'partner' who will escort me!
Boy who lies all the time

It seems that there is a boss at the bottom of this pond. My
cousin apparently saw it. It's a gigantic carp that swallows
people whole...!!
Is that so...?! What would happen if we get swallowed...?!
Boy who lies all the time

We can explore inside the body of the 'carp'! Apparently,
there is a legendary sword sleeping at the very back...!
That's what my cousin's older brother said!!

The legendary... sword...?! That's amazing... Your cousin's
older brother...!!

This is a hospital. There's a job opening for medical
assistance. I wonder if I should study and get hired too...

I've been told by my mom not to get close to the winter
water source. But it doesn't concern us, though. Hehe... I
feel like I've become a bad boy...!
The crystal stone 'Yukifuru' has been added to the transfer!

\SE[37]Uuu, it's so cold... so cold.... \SE[46]Oh, do you
need something? I can only sell accessories though...
